Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.53,English,,0,0,0,,- Can I tell you something I'm bad at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,跟大家分享一件我不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.50,English,,0,0,0,,I am terrible at making clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:05.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我非常不擅长当“标题党{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.65,English,,0,0,0,,Up until two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在两年前那会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.24,English,,0,0,0,,my most popular video was about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我最火的视频讲的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:12.01,English,,0,0,0,,a basketball being dropped from a dam with a bit of backspin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:12.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把回旋的篮球从水坝上扔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.78,English,,0,0,0,,It takes off like a rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,篮球像火箭一样飞出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.56,English,,0,0,0,,and shoots out way further than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞得比你想象的远得多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.19,English,,0,0,0,,This video was embedded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.70,English,,0,0,0,,on literally hundreds of news websites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个视频被几百个新闻网站转载
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.32,English,,0,0,0,,And in its first week, it got 16.3 million views,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在视频发出一个星期内获得了 1630 万次观看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:29.20,English,,0,0,0,,but almost none of those views came on the YouTube platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:29.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但来自油管平台本身的浏览量却寥寥无几
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.13,English,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.56,English,,0,0,0,,Because I gave it this thumbnail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这是我给它的封面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.91,English,,0,0,0,,and I called it "Strange Applications of the Magnus Effect."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并将其取名为「马格努斯效应的奇怪应用{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:39.63,English,,0,0,0,,This video is sponsored by KiwiCo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.12,English,,0,0,0,,More about them at the end of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.61,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I believe within YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我相信，这在油管圈子里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:47.24,English,,0,0,0,,I'm used as an example of how not to package your video.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:47.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是个“如何（不）包装自己视频”的典型例子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:50.32,English,,0,0,0,,As if to demonstrate just how bad a title and thumbnail this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:50.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像是为了反衬原来的标题和封面有多烂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.13,English,,0,0,0,,someone else re-uploaded the video with the clever title,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有人重投了我的视频  换了个聪明的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「从水坝上扔下的篮球」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:56.72,English,,0,0,0,,And within a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:56.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,短短几星期内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:01.01,English,,0,0,0,,that video had received tens of millions of views on YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:01.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个视频就在油管上获得了几千万浏览
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.41,English,,0,0,0,,This is when YouTube gave me access to ContentID.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这时候油管给了我 「ContentID」 的使用权限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.56,English,,0,0,0,,That's the system that allows you to earn revenue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.75,English,,0,0,0,,when someone else re-uploads your videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:07.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个权限让别人转载你的视频时  你能从中赚取收益
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:11.74,English,,0,0,0,,which was good, but I still wasn't very good at clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:11.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这很不错  但我还是不擅长当标题党
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.73,English,,0,0,0,,So for this video, I called in an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以本期视频  我请了一位专家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.65,English,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see your reaction face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想看看你的震惊脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.97,English,,0,0,0,,Can you give me like a reaction face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能否让我看看你的震惊脸{\fsp-30}？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.10,English,,0,0,0,,Like what's a good thumbnail face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,什么表情适合放封面上{\fsp-30}？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.15,English,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.09,English,,0,0,0,,This is a thumbnail face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是一个用作封面的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.28,English,,0,0,0,,I have like 10, I go through the motions of like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有十个这样的表情  就比如像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:31.06,English,,0,0,0,,And then we just take the best one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:31.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我们选择最好的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.56,English,,0,0,0,,I probably have like 500 of these just saved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我大概存了五百个像那样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.29,English,,0,0,0,,and we can just Photoshop my face on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我们直接 PS 这些表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.36,English,,0,0,0,,That way, I don't have to do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我就不用再做表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.46,English,,0,0,0,,- When I started on this platform, some 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约十年前，当我刚加入这个平台时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.12,English,,0,0,0,,clickbait was less important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,标题和封面没那么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.09,English,,0,0,0,,Subscribers were what mattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,重要的是粉丝数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.80,English,,0,0,0,,because most of the views came from the sub feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为大部分的点击  都来自向粉丝的推送
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:51.09,English,,0,0,0,,And videos went viral usually by getting a lot of attention elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:51.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,视频爆红一般是靠其他地方的流量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.00,English,,0,0,0,,like on Reddit or Facebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如 Reddit（红迪）或者 脸书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.86,English,,0,0,0,,not due to the YouTube algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而不是靠油管的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.81,English,,0,0,0,,But once you had a big video and people subscribed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但一旦你有个视频火了  吸引人们关注
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.28,English,,0,0,0,,well, then your next video would likely get a lot of views from those subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那你的下一个视频  很可能就会从粉丝那里得到很多浏览
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.42,English,,0,0,0,,So YouTube would take that popular video and share it with more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是油管就把热门的视频  分享给更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.72,English,,0,0,0,,And so you'd get more subscribers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样你会获得更多的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.24,English,,0,0,0,,in a positive feedback loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,形成一个正反馈循环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:11.06,English,,0,0,0,,But soon, YouTube realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.11,English,,0,0,0,,this did not create the best experience for the viewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:14.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但油管很快意识到  这给观众的体验并不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.05,English,,0,0,0,,They discovered that showing people only videos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,from channels they were subscribed to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们发现  光给人们展示他们订阅频道的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:22.69,English,,0,0,0,,led to fewer clicks, less watch time and less engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.25,English,,0,0,0,,with the site as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:24.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会导致网站的点击数、观看时间、互动量均整体下降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.25,English,,0,0,0,,Plus, they knew that relying on other platforms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.80,English,,0,0,0,,to drive traffic to viral hits was risky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:28.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,况且他们知道  靠其他平台引流创造爆红视频  有风险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.23,English,,0,0,0,,since those other platforms might disable the traffic at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为其他平台可以随时砍掉这些流量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.99,English,,0,0,0,,So they needed to make YouTube a destination in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以他们要让油管本身成为流量目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.00,English,,0,0,0,,They wanted people to come to YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们希望人们来到油管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.90,English,,0,0,0,,see videos that interested them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看他们感兴趣的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.62,English,,0,0,0,,click on at least one of them and watch it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,点击其中至少一个视频并看一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.43,English,,0,0,0,,Ideally get sucked down the YouTube rabbit hole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最好掉进油管的无底洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.77,English,,0,0,0,,and spend hours on the site without even noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不知不觉地在网站上花费数个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.61,English,,0,0,0,,The ultimate resource is people's time and attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最终极的资源  还是人们的时间和注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:56.43,English,,0,0,0,,and every platform is trying to capture as much of it as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:56.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,各大平台无不希望尽可能攫取用户的这些资源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.69,English,,0,0,0,,So, to make YouTube this go-to destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，为了让油管成为这个目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.42,English,,0,0,0,,they had decrease the importance of subscribers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们减少了粉丝的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.16,English,,0,0,0,,make it less like a podcast app
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.16,English,,0,0,0,,where you only get the shows you're subscribed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:05.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让它不像播客应用那样  只能收听已订阅的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.53,English,,0,0,0,,and more like Reddit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而是更像 Reddit（红迪）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,where stuff with the most engagement rises to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,互动最多的东西被顶到最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.74,English,,0,0,0,,But that necessarily meant increasing the importance of clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但那必然意味着  提高标题和封面的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.85,English,,0,0,0,,Now, there seems to be a paradox when it comes to clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但关于“标题党”却有一个矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.13,English,,0,0,0,,People almost universally claim to hate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.85,English,,0,0,0,,but you also see it everyhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:23.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“标题党”几乎人人喊打  却也随处可见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.60,English,,0,0,0,,So why is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.74,English,,0,0,0,,Well, one of the problems is we don't all agree
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.39,English,,0,0,0,,on the definition of clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其中一个问题在于  我们没有明确“标题党”的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.90,English,,0,0,0,,When I google it, the top definition is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在谷歌搜这个词的时候  第一条定义是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.24,English,,0,0,0,,on the internet, content whose main purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.79,English,,0,0,0,,is to attract attention and encourage visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:36.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在互联网上，用于吸引注意力、鼓励访客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.36,English,,0,0,0,,to click on a link to a particular webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,点击某个网页链接的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.05,English,,0,0,0,,We could call this type I clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以把它叫做「第一类标题党{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.41,English,,0,0,0,,and there doesn't seem to be anything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且它本身似乎没有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.98,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you didn't try to attract attention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,and get people to click on your links,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:48.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你不去吸引人们的注意力  让大家点击你的链接
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.40,English,,0,0,0,,then you wouldn't really be doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那等于没做你该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.29,English,,0,0,0,,But there is a second definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但“标题党”还可以指向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.95,English,,0,0,0,,One that I think more people ascribe to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一种我认为有更多人理解的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.41,English,,0,0,0,,which is something such as a headline designed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.76,English,,0,0,0,,to make readers want to click on a hyperlink,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:59.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一个让读者想去点击网页链接的东西  比如标题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.28,English,,0,0,0,,especially when the link leads to content of dubious value or interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尤其是链接到内容可疑的网页时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.09,English,,0,0,0,,Wikipedia says, "A defining characteristic of clickbait
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,维基百科说「标题党的一个根本特征是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.98,English,,0,0,0,,is that it is sensationalized or misleading."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,情绪化或有误导性{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,And it also talks about teasers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:15.64,English,,0,0,0,,that intentionally withhold information to exploit the "curiosity gap."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:15.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它还提到了一种故意卖关子  来吊人胃口的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.20,English,,0,0,0,,They give you enough information to make you curious,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它给你足够多的信息  来激发你的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.33,English,,0,0,0,,but not enough to satisfy that curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但不足以满足你的好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.06,English,,0,0,0,,Here are two actual titles from a news website.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这里是某新闻网站上的两个标题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:30.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《十个人中有九个人都不知道的惊人事实》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《给小孩们发了几把剪刀，然后......》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.20,English,,0,0,0,,I think we can all agree that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们都会认可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.47,English,,0,0,0,,these are examples of bad type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们属于坏的「第二类标题党{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.19,English,,0,0,0,,Now, imagine a clickbait space
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想像把各类“标题党”放在平面内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.83,English,,0,0,0,,where on one axis, you have how misleading or sensationalized it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,横轴描述的是它的误导性或者情绪化程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:48.98,English,,0,0,0,,And on the other, how much information is intentionally withheld
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.88,English,,0,0,0,,to create a curiosity gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,纵轴描述的是它为了设置悬念而隐瞒了多少信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.18,English,,0,0,0,,Well, then these two titles fall in the top right corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,刚才这两个标题就落在右上角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.74,English,,0,0,0,,And these are the zones of type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些就是第二类标题党所在的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.71,English,,0,0,0,,At the other extreme,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而在另一个极端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:02.73,English,,0,0,0,,you have things that are so unsensationalized as to be dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:02.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些标题是如此平淡  以至于有点枯燥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.55,English,,0,0,0,,You could call this the dead zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以把这边称作“盲区{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.72,English,,0,0,0,,Now, here is where you would find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在这片区域  你可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.65,English,,0,0,0,,"Strange applications of the Magnus Effect."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“马格努斯效应的奇特应用”之类的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.75,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, I didn't tell you what the applications were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为标题没有点明这些应用是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.98,English,,0,0,0,,Now, in the middle is where you would find type I clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,中间则是第一类标题党的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.48,English,,0,0,0,,But honestly, I think type I and type II clickbait are so different,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是讲真  这两类标题党有着巨大的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.99,English,,0,0,0,,that we shouldn't even use the same word for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大到我觉得不应该归结为同一个词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.60,English,,0,0,0,,Instead of type I clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,与其叫“第一类标题党{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.44,English,,0,0,0,,my friend and YouTuber, Brady Heron suggested legitbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一位油管主朋友 Brady Heron 认为  不如叫「合理标题党{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.31,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it might sound enticing, but it is legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这种标题听起来很诱人  但是并无误导性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.73,English,,0,0,0,,Instead of type II clickbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,与其叫“第二类标题党{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:40.35,English,,0,0,0,,we could use clicktrap, clicktrick, linktrap or dupechute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:40.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不如改称「点击陷阱 / 点击诡计 / 陷阱链接 / 整蛊链接」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.74,English,,0,0,0,,What's important to recognize is that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还要意识到一个重要的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:47.17,English,,0,0,0,,for any given video, there is no one true title and thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:47.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哪个视频都没有唯一准确的标题和封面图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.76,English,,0,0,0,,Each video could have hundreds or thousands of different legitbait titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每个视频都可以有成百上千各不相同的“合理标题{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.07,English,,0,0,0,,For example, how does a zero-G plane work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比方说《零重力飞机是如何运转的{\fsp-19}？{\fsp-30}》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,I went on a plane that does parabolic trajectories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《我坐上了一架沿抛物线飞行的飞机》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.97,English,,0,0,0,,What happens to fire on a zero-G plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《零重力飞机上的火焰是什么样的{\fsp-19}？{\r}》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.16,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the most enticing titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以发现，最有诱惑力（但合理）的标题和封面图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.15,English,,0,0,0,,are found close to type II clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,非常接近第二类标题党
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.69,English,,0,0,0,,I'm reminded of the infographic by smarter every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想起 SmarterEveryDay （另一位油管主）制作的一张图表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:13.62,English,,0,0,0,,showing that on social media, the greatest engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:13.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那张图表明  社交媒体上最有吸引力的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.95,English,,0,0,0,,occurs close to the boundary of what's allowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,都是在违法的边缘疯狂试探
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.19,English,,0,0,0,,But remember that everyone's definition of clickbait is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但要记住  每个人判断标题党的标准不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.97,English,,0,0,0,,and everyone's perceptions of words and images are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每个人对相同文字和图片的理解也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.85,English,,0,0,0,,So these are not clear boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这些类别并非泾渭分明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.20,English,,0,0,0,,They're actually kind of fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们之间的边界  事实上比较模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.27,English,,0,0,0,,What for one person might be legitbait,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,某人觉得是“合理标题党”的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.24,English,,0,0,0,,for someone else, could be a clicktrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在另一个人看来  可能就是“点击陷阱{\fsp-30}”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.96,English,,0,0,0,,What's clear is that on a site where click-through rate is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显然  在一个重视点击率的网站上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.27,English,,0,0,0,,clickbait of all types is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,出现这两类标题党都是难以避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:40.08,English,,0,0,0,,How important to a video's success is the title and thumbnail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:40.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,标题和封面  对一个视频的成功有多大帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.43,English,,0,0,0,,- Very important. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.43,English,,0,0,0,,If they don't click on the video, they don't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果观众不点进视频  他们压根看不到它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.90,English,,0,0,0,,You can't get 10 million views
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只有你获得了一千万点击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.10,English,,0,0,0,,unless 10 million people click on the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才有可能收获一千万的播放量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.93,English,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, it's literally that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  它就是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.63,English,,0,0,0,,They don't click on it, they don't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不点进去  何谈观看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.09,English,,0,0,0,,- So, why is clickbait everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  为何到处都是标题党呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.30,English,,0,0,0,,Well, because it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为它行之有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.70,English,,0,0,0,,More enticing thumbnails get more clicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,封面图越吸引人  收获的点击数越多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.43,English,,0,0,0,,Despite some people's claims that they won't click or they'll unsub,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管有人声称自己取关了、再也不点开这类视频
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.95,English,,0,0,0,,it's just like evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这机制类似于生物的演化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.10,English,,0,0,0,,Whatever survives, multiplies and traits become amplified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,生存竞争中的赢家就会保留、增殖  其特征会得到强化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.72,English,,0,0,0,,If you don't begrudge the giraffe its long neck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得长颈鹿的长脖子是它应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.63,English,,0,0,0,,so it can reach the highest leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.63,English,,0,0,0,,使它能吃到顶上的树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.07,English,,0,0,0,,can you begrudge a YouTuber the red arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.87,English,,0,0,0,,that allows them to reach further audiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:18.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那凭什么UP主就不能出奇招来吸引更多观众呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.00,English,,0,0,0,,I talked about this in my video two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,两年前我有期视频聊过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.44,English,,0,0,0,,To be successful as a YouTuber, you need to optimize two things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想当一个成功的UP主  需要优化两个数据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.14,English,,0,0,0,,watch time and the click-through rate of your videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,观看时长  以及视频的点击率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.73,English,,0,0,0,,That's the number of times the title and thumbnail are clicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.00,English,,0,0,0,,divided by the total number of times they're shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:32.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,即用户从视频封面点进去看的次数 除以 视频的总推送次数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.13,English,,0,0,0,,That's the number of impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,推送次数即为「曝光量{\fsp-30}」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:37.14,English,,0,0,0,,Now at the time, this was something of a revelation for me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:37.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个概念在当年让我耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.91,English,,0,0,0,,because I always thought my job was to make great videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我一直觉得  我的职责就是制作优质的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.84,English,,0,0,0,,And then a title and thumbnail that adequately represented what the video was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有能恰当呈现视频主旨的标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:49.22,English,,0,0,0,,But now I've realized that making the title and thumbnail is at least half the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:49.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我现在意识到  构思标题和封面费的工夫不亚于做视频
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,This is not just because better titles and thumbnails get you more clicks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这不只是因为  更好的标题和封面能带来更多点击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.16,English,,0,0,0,,but because better titles and thumbnails will get you way more impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还因为它们可以给你带来多得多的曝光量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,YouTube has limited real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,油管得在有限的地盘里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.28,English,,0,0,0,,with which to show you virtually infinite content.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,给你推送几乎无穷多的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.22,English,,0,0,0,,And so it's not enough to make a good video even if people watch all of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,仅仅做出让观众愿意看完的好视频  是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.19,English,,0,0,0,,you also have to make a title and thumbnail that gets clicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你还得搞个能吸引人点击的标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.70,English,,0,0,0,,especially in competition with other really good titles and thumbnails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才能在一众优秀的标题和封面中  脱颖而出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.54,English,,0,0,0,,That's the only way you can expect YouTube to give you more impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要想在油管得到更高曝光量  你别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.28,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the big development since my last video on this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,自从我上次做同样话题的视频后，油管有个大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.87,English,,0,0,0,,is YouTube introduced real-time metrics
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它引进了实时的度量指标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.68,English,,0,0,0,,like views, impressions and click-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,包括观看次数，曝光量和点击率等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.03,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I suggested this would create an arms race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得  这会带来一场创作者的军备竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:31.02,English,,0,0,0,,So what you can bet will happen is that creators will launch a video
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:31.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几乎可以肯定  接下来的创作者在发布视频后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:34.02,English,,0,0,0,,and then they'll be sitting there with all these different variants of thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:34.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就会一直鼓捣各种不同的封面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.75,English,,0,0,0,,and they'll be swapping them out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再把不同封面换来换去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.40,English,,0,0,0,,and looking at what that does to click-through rate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看看对点击率有什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:42.79,English,,0,0,0,,and then going with the one that leads to the greatest click-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:42.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最后敲定使用点击率最高的封面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.40,English,,0,0,0,,And this is basically what has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现状基本上就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.66,English,,0,0,0,,Let me give you my favorite example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,举个我最喜欢的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.27,English,,0,0,0,,Last year, I made a video about asteroids,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,去年底我做了一期讲小行星的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.71,English,,0,0,0,,which I thought was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这期我自己感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.62,English,,0,0,0,,I called it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我给的标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《小行星：地球受到的最大威胁》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.10,English,,0,0,0,,which is something Stephen Hawking said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,语出史蒂芬·霍金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.20,English,,0,0,0,,And people were very positive about the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,观众对这个视频的评价很积极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.20,English,,0,0,0,,They thought it was maybe one of my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们觉得  这有望跻身我最受欢迎的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.19,English,,0,0,0,,but the performance was well below average.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但其播放量让人大跌眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:09.28,English,,0,0,0,,In its first day, asteroids was ranked ninth out of my previous 10 videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:09.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,上线第一天  在我最近十部作品里  它的播放量为倒数第二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:13.27,English,,0,0,0,,It was probably on target for about one and a half million views.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:13.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样下去  这期视频的播放量预计在150万左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.06,English,,0,0,0,,So I tried different titles and thumbnails like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是  我尝试了不同的标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:18.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《小行星撞击：我们有多少机会{\fsp-19}？{\r}》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《小行星撞击：我们能做什么{\fsp-19}？{\r}》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.85,English,,0,0,0,,But none of these changes got much traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这些改动没有什么吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.75,English,,0,0,0,,And then on day three after launch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但到了第三天中午
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.99,English,,0,0,0,,I changed the title and thumbnail to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把标题和封面改成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《这些小行星撞击地球才是我们真正得担心的》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7}BV1TK4y1L7x9
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.72,English,,0,0,0,,And immediately the video started doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这则视频立刻就有了起色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:38.92,English,,0,0,0,,It quickly shot up from almost my worst performing video to my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:38.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它很快就从我表现最差劲的视频之一变成了最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:42.22,English,,0,0,0,,It now has 14 million views.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:42.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在它已经有1400万次观看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.02,English,,0,0,0,,Nothing about the video changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,视频本身没有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.33,English,,0,0,0,,just that one image and 38 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,仅仅是换了一张封面图片和一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:50.55,English,,0,0,0,,But because of that, the video has reached nearly 10 times
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.82,English,,0,0,0,,as many people as it otherwise would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:52.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正因如此，这个视频的人气比改之前高出了十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,And the title and thumbnail accurately describe what the video is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且标题和封面准确地描述了视频的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.70,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure, there's a curiosity gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然 标题里确实是卖了个关子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.55,English,,0,0,0,,but you couldn't explain the whole concept in the length of the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过你没法在标题中就能完全说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.55,English,,0,0,0,,So if you see a YouTuber changing titles and thumbnails,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以如果你看到一个UP主改了标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.07,English,,0,0,0,,this is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.44,English,,0,0,0,,Because that effort can be rewarded many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这种做法能得到数倍的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.25,English,,0,0,0,,I've seen people objecting to this practice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也见到有人反对这种做法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.99,English,,0,0,0,,because they think the creator is trying to dupe their audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他们认为这么做是在欺骗观众
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.97,English,,0,0,0,,get them to click on the same video more than once,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让他们重复点击一个视频多次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.97,English,,0,0,0,,but that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是事情并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.91,English,,0,0,0,,The whole point is to get YouTube to show the title and thumbnail to more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关键在于让视频平台向更多的人展示标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.87,English,,0,0,0,,We're trying to increase the number of impressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们这样做 是为了提高视频的展示次数
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.63,English,,0,0,0,,which is heavily dependent on the click-through rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这个次数严重依赖点击率
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.47,English,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of my recent videos have this typical view curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最近我的许多视频都有这种典型的观看曲线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.91,English,,0,0,0,,There's an initial spike after I release the video
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我发布视频之初会火一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.00,English,,0,0,0,,and then a dip,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,之后是一段低谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.34,English,,0,0,0,,and then a second bump after I have figured out a better title and thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,, 在当我想到更好的标题和封面之后，观看量又有明显上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:44.15,English,,0,0,0,,I change the title and thumbnail and I watch the real time view graph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:44.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我换掉标题和封面，然后观察实时播放量统计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.71,English,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for is a noticeable bump in views.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我期望的是观看量会有明显的增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.28,English,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there's no change, sometimes it gets worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是有时候并没有变好 可能还会更差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.95,English,,0,0,0,,but on occasions, when you see something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但有时也会看到这样的图像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.52,English,,0,0,0,,well then, you know you've found a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这说明你成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.06,English,,0,0,0,,This is something all the big YouTubers are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是所有知名油管主都在做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.11,English,,0,0,0,,Not even Mr. Beast knows exactly which thumbnail will work best beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,即使Mr. Beast也没法事先知道哪个封面是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Mr. Beast：粉丝最多的美国油管主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.58,English,,0,0,0,,Have you ever changed a title and thumbnail and then the video did better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,-你有没有过换完标题封面后，视频表现更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.76,English,,0,0,0,,- Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,-哦 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,So everybody, I usually make like two or three thumbnails,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一般制作两三个封面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.30,English,,0,0,0,,and then if it's not doing as well as I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果一上来没有达到想要的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.82,English,,0,0,0,,we usually just swap 'em out and see if it does better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我通常会换个标题封面看看有没有改善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.91,English,,0,0,0,,'cause the thing is like, you don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为除非你开挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.42,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, you could know if you just were an almighty being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你不可能知道人们感兴趣什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.04,English,,0,0,0,,that could just predict what people would be interested in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你只能猜他们会对什么感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.50,English,,0,0,0,,but you know, usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是 通常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.58,English,,0,0,0,,Like, you can do hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说 你整了个捉迷藏的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:29.03,English,,0,0,0,,You don't really know if like you hiding in a tree
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.06,English,,0,0,0,,and then someone walking below you is a good thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:31.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,封面可以是 你藏在树上 树下有个人走过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.58,English,,0,0,0,,Or if you hide in a trash can and them walking in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者藏在垃圾箱里 他们从你前面走过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.94,English,,0,0,0,,So, you know, just do both
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不知道哪个好  就两者都试试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.43,English,,0,0,0,,and then see which one interests people a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看看哪个更能激起人们的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.19,English,,0,0,0,,- I feel the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:42.29,English,,0,0,0,,but I do feel like you have a better sense of this than like most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:42.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我觉得跟大部分人相比，你对此有更好的把握
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:42.91,English,,0,0,0,,- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:42.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.59,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, no one gets 40 million views a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要不然人人都一个视频4000万次播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.36,English,,0,0,0,,- But what is the point in getting more views?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是更多播放是为了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.19,English,,0,0,0,,If you're cynical,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得人皆利己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.81,English,,0,0,0,,you might say it's all about money and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可能会说这都是为了名利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.20,English,,0,0,0,,And while there are certainly financial incentives to getting more views,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而其中固然有经济上的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.86,English,,0,0,0,,that's not why I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这并不是我追求更多观看的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.36,English,,0,0,0,,As an educational YouTuber,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,作为一个教育向的UP主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.37,English,,0,0,0,,I think there are two very good reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为有两个比较重要的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:07.11,English,,0,0,0,,for using excellent type I clickbait over more straightforward packaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:07.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们应该用一类标题党  来代替平铺直叙的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.79,English,,0,0,0,,To understand the first reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第一个原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.57,English,,0,0,0,,let's consider two different possible titles for my most recent video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,先来看看我上一期视频  草拟的两个不同标题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:16.02,English,,0,0,0,,I called it "The Simplest Math Problem No One Can Solve,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:16.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一个标题是 「这道看似简单的数学题没有人解得出来{\fsp-30}」 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:16.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7}BV1Ty4y1778o
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.35,English,,0,0,0,,but it's a video about the Collatz conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这视频是有关角谷猜想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.47,English,,0,0,0,,So perhaps a more straightforward title
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以一个更直接的标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.81,English,,0,0,0,,would have been simply to call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就直接写角谷猜想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.50,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is, if I publish a video called the Collatz conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题在于，如果我发布一则名为角谷猜想的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.45,English,,0,0,0,,the most likely people to click on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.64,English,,0,0,0,,are those who already know what the Collatz conjecture is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:31.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最可能点进来看的  是那些已经知道角谷猜想的人
