Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.02,English,,0,0,0,,and only the very curious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只有他们中抱有相当好奇心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.80,English,,0,0,0,,or those who really like Veritasium would click.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者真理元素的老粉才会点击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.56,English,,0,0,0,,In contrast, calling it "The Simplest Math Problem No One Can Solve,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,相比之下 把它叫做 「这道看似简单的数学题没有人解得出来{\fsp-30}」
