Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.94,English,,0,0,0,,in the world by the maximum amount possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来提升世界人民的知识水平
