Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.05,English,,0,0,0,,The second reason we need to optimize titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,另一个需要优化标题和封面的原因是
