Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.89,English,,0,0,0,,YouTuber and Patreon CEO, Jack Conte
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Jack Conte, Patreon（一个供内容创建者进行群众募资的平台） 的 CEO  也是一位油管主
