Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,so I can make the type of videos that are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如此一来  我才能制作出我心目中地位甚高的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.59,English,,0,0,0,,Now, is it ironic that a channel whose whole purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么 如果现在有个频道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.42,English,,0,0,0,,is to promote a true seeking mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它旨在为人们培养求真心理
