Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.42,English,,0,0,0,,So here is an old video that I originally entitled,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我最初给一个老视频起的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「为什么说中子是核物理的英雄」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.84,English,,0,0,0,,In hindsight, it's a weird, kinda meaningless title.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,事后看来  这个标题显得很奇怪  毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.49,English,,0,0,0,,So I changed it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我把标题换成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「爱因斯坦为何认为没法造出核武器」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.87,English,,0,0,0,,It's clearer, more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个标题更清晰  更精确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:30.51,English,,0,0,0,,And this is what happened to views after the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:30.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我改了标题之后  播放量的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.41,English,,0,0,0,,I changed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「马格努斯效应的奇怪用法」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.17,English,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,改成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「在水坝上来一个后旋投篮」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.83,English,,0,0,0,,Again, more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也改得更精确了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.83,English,,0,0,0,,And the video is now being watched on YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后现在这个视频在 YouTube 上的播放量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.72,English,,0,0,0,,probably 10 million more views than it otherwise would have had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比我修改标题之前涨了 1000 多万呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.44,English,,0,0,0,,Even anti-clickbait has proven effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,事实证明非标题党类型的标题也是可以发挥作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.36,English,,0,0,0,,Here's a video I originally titled,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我最初给这个视频起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.60,English,,0,0,0,,"Are Negative Ions Good For You?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,「负离子对人真的有好处吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.05,English,,0,0,0,,Which is a question nobody asked ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是个此前没人问过的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.64,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I changed it to, "Do Salt Lamps Work?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我改成了「离子灯对人真的有用吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,（没用.jpg）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.40,English,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,认真讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.93,English,,0,0,0,,And here's the result:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是它换了名字的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.94,English,,0,0,0,,One and a half million more views.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,涨了 150 多万播放量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.62,English,,0,0,0,,I think looking at these examples,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得 通过观察这些变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.93,English,,0,0,0,,you could easily make the case
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以很容易得出结论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.98,English,,0,0,0,,that YouTube has made me better at what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,油管让我在制作视频这方面更上一层楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:17.00,English,,0,0,0,,It has improved the clarity and accuracy of my titles and thumbnails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:17.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它使我的标题和封面更加清楚、准确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.67,English,,0,0,0,,It's helped me figure out what is interesting to my audience
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还让我摸清了  观众对什么内容感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:24.23,English,,0,0,0,,and how to encapsulate that in a single image and fewer than 50 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:24.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及如何将内容浓缩为一张图和 50 字母内的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.22,English,,0,0,0,,For those of you who worry that a focus on titles and thumbnails
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有观众会担心  我重视标题和封面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:30.58,English,,0,0,0,,will prevent me from picking challenging science topics,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:30.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可能会让我选一些  不那么有挑战性的科学话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:33.01,English,,0,0,0,,well, I simply ask you to look at the videos
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:33.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得，我还是要请你们去看看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.44,English,,0,0,0,,from the last year or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,近一两年发布的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.58,English,,0,0,0,,like the ones on Gödel's incompleteness theorem,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如那个讲哥德尔不完备定理的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.56,English,,0,0,0,,general relativity, Penrose tilings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有广义相对论  彭罗斯密铺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.72,English,,0,0,0,,the logistic map, Newton's method of calculating Pi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,单峰映射  还有牛顿的逼近圆周率的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.64,English,,0,0,0,,the one way speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和测量单程光速的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.53,English,,0,0,0,,Good titles and thumbnails make it possible to tackle these topics
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的标题封面可以紧扣主题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.79,English,,0,0,0,,and to reach more people who have heard of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能让视频被推送给更多的听过此话题的观众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.63,English,,0,0,0,,There is a symbiotic relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,视频的播放量和视频内容的质量之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.16,English,,0,0,0,,between views and video quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有着紧密的相互依存的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.98,English,,0,0,0,,The more views we get, the more people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，有了更多的播放量，我们才能付出更多的人力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.10,English,,0,0,0,,locations, props and equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使用更多更好的场地 道具和设备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.29,English,,0,0,0,,and research we can invest in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并进行更缜密的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.44,English,,0,0,0,,This makes the next video better than the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这才能让下一期视频的质量比之前任何一期都要好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.62,English,,0,0,0,,If we can be good at titles and thumbnails,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么如果我们可以掌握想出好的标题封面的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.58,English,,0,0,0,,the ultimate outcome is better videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么最终一定就能做出更好的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.21,English,,0,0,0,,That is something I think you and I both want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为这就是你我共同追求的目标
